<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Middle Valley Community Bank</h1>
    <p class="lead">Middle Valley Community Bank offers the first-ever web-based ATM.
    Give it a try today! </p>
    <p><a href="http://asp.net" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Powered by ASP.NET &raquo;</a></p>
